Sentencas: Fibrous perovskite oxide has been the most promising cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) due to its efficient mass and charge transfer.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Herein, a core-shell fiber-structured YCo0.5Fe0.5O3 (YCF)- Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) cathode is synthesized via the modified electrospinning technique.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: These unique YCF-GDC fibers exhibit a uniform diameter of 300 nm, and the GDC particles are attached to the YCF fiber cores.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance demonstrates a relatively low area-specific resistance of 0.66 Omega.cm(2) at 550 degrees C in air, which is much lower than 1.56 Omega.cm(2) of pure YCF fiber cathode.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Moreover, the distribution of relaxation times (DRT) analysis results indicate that the introduction of GDC nanoparticles and the core-shell structure greatly facilitate oxygen-ion conduction and charge transfer processes, and the oxygen incorporation process plays a major role in the total polarization resistance.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The NiO-GDCIGDCIfibrous YCF-GDC fuel cell shows a maximum power density of 426.5 mW.cm(-1) at 550 degrees C. These results display that the core-shell fiber-structured YCF- GDC composite oxide is a promising candidate of highly active cathode for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Electrospun Core-Shell Fibers for High-Efficient Composite Cathode-Based Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
